'''Powerlevel9k''' is a theme for ZSH which uses Powerline Fonts. It can be used with vanilla ZSH or ZSH frameworks such as Oh-My-Zsh, Prezto, Antigen, and many others.

== Installation ==

=== Prerequisites ===

Powerlevel9k theme use {{Package|app-shells/zsh}}.

=== USE flags ===

{{USEflag|package=app-shells/zsh-theme-powerlevel9k}}

=== Emerge ===

To install {{Package|app-shells/zsh-theme-powerlevel9k}}:

{{Emerge|app-shells/zsh-theme-powerlevel9k}}

== Configuration ==

After you have configured zsh correctly, add this command at the begin of your zshrc file to source Powerlevel9k theme:

{{FileBox|filename=~/.zshrc|lang=bash|1=
source "/usr/share/zsh-theme-powerlevel9k/powerlevel9k.zsh-theme"
}}

See git Powerlevel9k repository to configure more this theme: https://github.com/Powerlevel9k/powerlevel9k.

